<p>The trailer sees him making a constant stream of complaints to the local police officers who keep blowing him off for crying wolf. </p>

<p>On Halloween, Hubie kicks things up a notch as a self-appointed volunteer protector and sets out to make sure everyone is on the straight and narrow.</p>

<p>'It's pretty impressive how long he's been a loser,' Maya Rudolf quips while dressed like the bride of Frankenstein.</p>

